    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and dice</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong>, chop your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> roughly and peel your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong> and bash into small rough pieces</p><p>Tip: Don't have a pestle & mortar? Pulse in a food processor!</p>",
