    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced shallot </strong>and<strong> diced pepper </strong>with the <strong>bashed</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> <strong>&</strong> <strong>chilli</strong> (can’t handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the<strong> chopped free range chicken</strong> and cook for a further 4 min</p>",
